{"id": "1247447827227873310", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "總而言之昨天腦袋裡突然閃過一個腦洞大開的小推測，覺得如果真的是這樣的話感覺超帶感⋯⋯所以就想發上來分享一下，完全是沒有根據的！雖然感覺放考據不太好但我也不確定放哪裡好！\n\n我會把腦洞打在留言區，先講清楚這一切都是我的妄想+藍色窗簾！但還是歡迎跟我一起妄想！", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:12:18.471000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😭", "emoji_id": null, "count": 12}], "attachments": [{"id": "1247447827421073408", "filename": "E0FCD7E1-404E-4DDB-BCF1-B5C5E56B6A57.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 384384, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1247447827227873310/1247447827421073408/E0FCD7E1-404E-4DDB-BCF1-B5C5E56B6A57.jpg?ex=69ccc552&is=69cb73d2&hm=fec79a740e6d60071e9eeeae55a658eb5087b16dd5485d59b3958eff98eb4460&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247447909490884688", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "呃就是，戈利亞的本源是群鯊之父這點應該是無可爭辯的了。\n但我就在想啊，為什麼他的尾巴不是鯊魚⋯？\n\n所以就突然腦洞大開，他的尾巴會不會其實有更諷刺的意味⋯？（當然不排除是只有一條鯊魚尾看起來沒氣勢）\n\n就是，你想啊⋯ 其實是可以給他鯊魚尾巴的吧，但偏偏給了他跟圖魯一樣的章魚觸手（雖然有多了尖刺\n\n不覺得有種偽造品的味道嗎？", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:12:38.084000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247448490900983839", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "有跟王一樣的觸肢但群鯊之父終究只是克蘇魯的化身⋯⋯", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:14:56.703000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247448773068591164", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "戈利亞你是不是永遠無法成為王啊我要哭了😭", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:16:03.977000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247450164923338795", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "當然之前有人推測他是群鯊之父+少量達貢\n但我翻了一下，（考據不精敬請見諒）達貢的形象基本上是半人半魚，聖經中的形象甚至下半身是魚尾。感覺怎麼樣戈利亞有一條鯊魚尾巴都會更直觀，但他是⋯章魚觸手⋯⋯😭", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:21:35.821000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:23:01.599000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247453374547361802", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "422799061133950978", "author_name": "ernest_heart", "author_bot": false, "content": "還記得鯊魚潛遊裡的巨人之歌嗎？\n暴虐的巨人是被創造來讓神打敗，好彰顯神的正義與力量的🥹", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:34:21.055000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😭", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247454339291807755", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 19, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "我要尖叫了我去撞牆我不活了😭", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:38:11.068000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["422799061133950978"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1247453374547361802", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247454993007509505", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "總覺得真的超諷刺的⋯⋯\n相似的觸手⋯相似的實力（我覺得他們兩個應該勉強可以五五開啦）⋯但很遺憾你身上沒有神之血脈所以深潛者不會聽你的，你終究是個偽造品⋯⋯", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:40:46.926000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247455678394794065", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "說實在的戈利亞如此渴望權力，但遊戲當下的世界裡我覺得並沒有他渴望的東西也沒人能給他⋯⋯所以我是真的蠻好奇之後他的戲份到底會怎麼寫⋯因為他在追求的其實一直是個接近不存在也不可能實現的東西⋯⋯", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T07:43:30.335000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1nekoomglol", "emoji_id": "1206774391858405409", "count": 7}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
