{"id": "1247560657327489136", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 19, "author_id": "777861907973406731", "author_name": "yolo_mode", "author_bot": false, "content": "我被我自己的腦洞刀死....", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T14:40:39.263000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1004313148637052948"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1247459700463636570", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247562873337544754", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "1209525934839955491", "author_name": "unmasked0406", "author_bot": false, "content": "就像彌利亞姆身為最虔誠的信徒卻沒辦法成為神母一樣\n戈利亞的力量再怎麼高也成不了神王⋯⋯（但沒關係我好愛他", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T14:49:27.601000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-06-04T14:49:57.978000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247583139350577322", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "因為長觸手才是深海的象徵\n魚尾巴代表深海之力不夠純\n沒錯 我就是在臭凱刻斯", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T16:09:59.395000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247583400148074566", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "認真說就是 克蘇魯沒長個觸手都不敢說自己位格夠高（X", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T16:11:01.574000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247584729633656915", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "1232289638484541472", "author_name": "xiyuejintianbuchouqia_85237", "author_bot": false, "content": "可能，戈利亚是弥妈唤醒的，然后弥妈是信秃噜的，所以唤醒鲨鱼的时候加了一堆触手，简称夹带私货", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T16:16:18.548000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247587135826038956", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "應該說 其實所謂“深海之力”的成份跟神奇\n “利莫里亞的力量”包含了神王.祭司.萬民\n力量由上到下的同時 承認也從由下到上賦予權利\n“王權”就是基於萬民的承認跟膜拜才被賦予類似“神權”的懲戒能力", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T16:25:52.229000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1247587674097979443", "channel_id": "1247447827227873310", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "傻鯊就算篡奪 要成為深潛者之王還需要受萬民的認可與朝拜\n🫠哭哭喔  連一個部落都被背叛", "timestamp": "2024-06-04T16:28:00.563000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1247447827227873310", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "［腦洞］偽王論", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
